_sText: This is an updated version version of the map ka_soccer_2008_indoor_beta1. It now has a scoreboard and radar, a gap where you can get on the outside of the nets (and walk back in anywhere, although i'm thinking of changing that), And the change rooms / toilet rooms have been made hollow and filled with toilets and seats etc. It's also been optimized, you should get better fps than the previous version or fletch's original. For those that haven't seen the older version of this, you can jump into the nets and spring back, like with real indoor nets. There's still a fair bit to be done on this map, but this is a step forward.
